      "contentFieldValue": {
        "data": "<h2 id=\"h_01J01S57EVQ2V7C6P36Z9Z4S3K\">Liferay Cloud Security Alert: June 2019</h2>\n\n<p><span>The following issue may compromise the security of your Liferay SaaS environment.</span></p>\n\n<h2 id=\"h_01J01S57EVE9KM4BXDNZQK2RQF\">Vulnerability Information</h2>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li><a href=\"https://help.liferay.com/hc/articles/360029720152\" target=\"_self\">18-VULN</a>: Build system credentials are exposed to collaborators of the project</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Please see the <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><a href=\"https://help.liferay.com/hc/en-us/articles/360018875952#DXP-cloud\">Liferay Cloud Security Advisories</a></span> section for more information on the vulnerability.</p>"
      },
